        "description": {
            "value": "<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DetailedOutput\"><strong>Prerequisites</strong> Halcyon Speaker Dedication<br></span></p>\n<hr>\n<p>You can cast <a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"pf2e.spells-srd\" data-id=\"TUj8eugNqAvB1vVR\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Creation</a> as an innate spell at will, choosing whether it is arcane or primal each time. The created object lasts until you spend 1 hour not within its immediate vicinity or until it is destroyed. Such objects are called persistent creations. If you cast <em>creation</em> again, any persistent creation you previously created with the spell immediately disintegrates.&nbsp;</p>",
